{"tid":964600,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港樂壇永遠唔會上到大台","createTime":"2019-01-01T12:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T02:22:43.000Z","uid":17232,"like":63,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"196fbd9cebd7cb2a8af56f980d02202d1025f43a","tid":964600,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"香港十幾年黎都無乜出過男子偶像組合<br />\n依家難得香港有個偶像組合係睇得吓。起碼上台表演比外國人睇到都唔會覺得奇撚怪，唔會一岩一忽。<br />\n<br />\n點知啲連登毒撚見到人地靚仔少少就起曬鋼<br />\n啲毒撚真係廢撚閪人種黎<br />\n<br />\n自從mirror出道幾個月黎，出面啲post係講乜？<br />\n1. 總之睇姜濤個樣就唔方係好人啦<br />\n2. 呢啲人唔值得尊重，你係奸嘅個樣幾好都係奸<br />\n3. 佢同啲廣告真係好唔match囉 總之就係好撚cringe啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好話我直接講出你地心裡面嘅諗法喇，根本全部都係無point咁為踩鳩人而踩鳩人，目的就係滿足自己自己唔抵得人嘅心<br />\n最好香港啲偶像個個都同你地一樣咁撚毒咁撚樣衰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7dd7a8903f7a85834c4a4a5b4cc92a2dbbea2e","tid":964600,"uid":17232,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"等全世界睇吓香港人係咩品味 捧啲咩奇奇怪怪嘅人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4560e390ad52504a3b502783e2c7c0bda914eaaf","tid":964600,"uid":17232,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T12:26:36.000Z","msg":"啲毒撚淨係夠膽喺到負評唔撚出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd7f45d9d8933ec1753790a719c9d843bc42c5c","tid":964600,"uid":134936,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ff7dd7a8903f7a85834c4a4a5b4cc92a2dbbea2e","tid":964600,"uid":17232,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"等全世界睇吓香港人係咩品味 捧啲咩奇奇怪怪嘅人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"G-Dragon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a243c9c0eb312c521de1981a6c534cba4794ce","tid":964600,"uid":31215,"like":25,"dislike":6,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":